issue.title: Voting mechanism (DAO)
issue.body:
People, who already burn token has voting rights, to decide, which token add to the pool!

Welcome to discuss  Voting policy below! 👍

issue.title: Burn with ETH Donation
issue.body:
If you don' have a shit coin: you can donate ETH to someone who will burn that coin!

## Donation distribution:

1/2 to someone who burns this coin (by moon math from @snjax)

1/2 to whole burning donation pool for people, who burn!
